00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 5=

4
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,960
(Yuehui Pavilion)
I told you to stop outsiders.

5
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,160
Are you deaf?

6
00:01:11,420 --> 00:01:13,880
Since your ears are so useless,
we might as well cut them off.

7
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,160
Young Lady, have mercy.

8
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:22,520
Which palace

9
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,480
are you from?

10
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,920
Fourth Young Lady, please calm down.

11
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,600
Ruyan

12
00:01:29,610 --> 00:01:32,500
was just recently bestowed the title
of Lady of Gentleness by His Majesty.

13
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,320
Lady of Gentleness?

14
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,400
You cannot hit me.

15
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,220
My sister is
Lady Liu of Bright Deportment.

16
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,640
So what if she's Lady Liu?

17
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,120
My father is the Duke.

18
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,040
And my sister is the Empress.

19
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,640
Trying to compare status with me?

20
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,320
Who gave you the nerve?

21
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,440
By the Empress's decree,

22
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,380
anyone who disrupts
the grand dance performance

23
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,760
shall be executed immediately.

24
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,840
As for you,

25
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,080
you can add some color

26
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,200
to my green silk.

27
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,800
Hit her harder!

28
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,220
I thought she was something special.

29
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,190
But she can't even
dodge this simple bullying.

30
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,240
Didn't Your Majesty notify the Empress?

31
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,960
Why hasn't Her Majesty arrived yet?

32
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,440
Your Majesty, are you not going
to intervene?

33
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:59,080
Nangong Xuanyu is the most powerful

34
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,720
and most heroic man

35
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,880
in the world.

36
00:03:06,210 --> 00:03:07,600
I suppose the Empress isn't coming.

37
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,000
Go and tell them to stop.

38
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,520
Lady of Bright Deportment has arrived.

39
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,120
Stop this at once.

40
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,320
It seems I don't need to help.

41
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,440
She can handle the harem on her own.

42
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:32,720
Jiang Wanning, how dare you use
private torture in the palace?

43
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,120
I...

44
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:35,360
I have the Jinfeng Token.

45
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,240
How insolent!

46
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,800
You dare to be so arrogant before me?

47
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:46,880
Today, I'll see exactly
how you plan to hit me.

48
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,040
Forget it.

49
00:03:57,720 --> 00:04:00,240
You aren't worthy of being
handled by me personally.

50
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,680
Someone, come.

51
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,640
Send the Fourth Young Lady Jiang
to the Empress's palace.

52
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,520
What if I refuse to go?

53
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,880
Then I shall invite
the Empress's carriage

54
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,040
here to the Shanglin Garden.

55
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,960
You!

56
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:18,880
Let's go.

57
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,640
Young Lady...

58
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,360
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

59
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,120
Shen Zhinian,

60
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,920
I saved you this once today.

61
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,600
I might not next time.

62
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,080
Put away your little tricks.

63
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,160
In this palace,

64
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,320
the more schemes you have,

65
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,200
the shorter your life will be.

66
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:01,920
Liu...

67
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:14,240
Finally, the planting
is almost finished.

68
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,080
Young Lady,

69
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,920
everyone in this palace is a predator,

70
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,200
ruthless and cruel.

71
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,080
You have such a weak personality.

72
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:31,120
How are we ever going
to survive in this palace?

73
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,600
It doesn't matter.

74
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,520
These are just superficial wounds.

75
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,560
Come.

76
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,290
There's important
business to take care of.

77
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,720
You're already injured like this.

78
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,820
What else do you need to do?

79
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:42,880
To vent my anger.

80
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,520
Today's grievance

81
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,920
will be settled today.

82
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,280
Are you alright?

83
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,680
Who is it?

84
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,040
Who's there?

85
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,920
Stop hitting me.

86
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:02,720
Who is it?

87
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,840
Who's that?

88
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,960
Are you alright, Young Lady?

89
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,760
Why is it always me who gets hurt?

90
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,760
We have no grudge against Liu Ruyan.

91
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,200
Why would she do this?

92
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:22,520
Women in the palace will
make things difficult for each other

93
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,990
before they gain the Emperor's favor.

94
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:26,640
If even the Empress
and Lady Liu are like this,

95
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:29,000
it's even more so for
someone like Liu Ruyan.

96
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,920
Senior Attendant,
a letter was found at the door.

97
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:46,700
(Jianyue Pavilion,
Shanglin Garden. Zhen.)

98
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:50,120
(If he hadn't left me alone
in the liquor cellar,)

99
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:52,400
(none of this would be happening.)

100
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,320
I'm not going.

101
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,800
Your Majesty,

102
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:01,230
the Empress has removed
her hairpin to plead for mercy.

103
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,670
She brought Jiang Wanning
and has been kneeling for 15 minutes.

104
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,840
Her Majesty's health is already poor.

105
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,900
If she continues to kneel,

106
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,680
I'm afraid her body won't hold up.

107
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,960
If Duke Zhen uses
this to stir up trouble,

108
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:12,040
Your Majesty might be harassed again.

109
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,600
This kneeling display of hers

110
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,760
isn't meant for me to see.

111
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,360
(Yuehui Pavilion)
I was lenient in disciplining my sister.

112
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,490
She has made a grave mistake.

113
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,160
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

114
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:31,200
I was lenient in disciplining my sister.

115
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,600
She has made a grave mistake.

116
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,280
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

117
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,040
Your Majesty.

118
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,320
Your Majesty.

119
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,520
Your Majesty.

120
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,720
Your Majesty,

121
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,460
His Majesty asks that you return.

122
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,240
This is
Fourth Young Lady Jiang's matter,

123
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,990
and it has nothing to do with you.

124
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,640
I watched her grow up.

125
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,080
If she is at fault,

126
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,760
it means I didn't teach her well.

127
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,440
Your Majesty,

128
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,560
for my sake,

129
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,960
please let Wanning
kowtow and apologize to you.

130
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,320
Your Majesty,

131
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,280
I know my mistake.

132
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,360
I won't dare do it again.

133
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,240
Come in.

134
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,360
Your Majesty...

135
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,600
Whether His Majesty can forgive you

136
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,000
depends on your attitude.

137
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,160
You must apologize sincerely.

138
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,400
Otherwise, even I can't help you,

139
00:08:35,410 --> 00:08:37,380
and you'll have to
return to the Jiang residence.

140
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,760
I can't go back.

141
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,280
Father would beat me to death.

142
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,760
Your Majesty,

143
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,000
I know my mistake.

144
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,590
I beg for Your Majesty's forgiveness.

145
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,280
Your Majesty,

146
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,960
Wanning knows she was wrong.

147
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,960
For my sake and my brother's,

148
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,880
please let Wanning stay by my side.

149
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,320
Let her accompany me
through my final days.

150
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,800
Jiang Wanning,

151
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,640
since the Empress has pleaded for you,

152
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,880
I will forgive you this once.

153
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,400
Thank you, Your Majesty.

154
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,880
It's getting late.

155
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,520
Escort the Empress back to her palace.

156
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,240
I know why Father
wanted you to enter the palace,

157
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:20,600
but there was no need to be so hasty.

158
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,600
I protected you today,

159
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,440
but I'm afraid His Majesty

160
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,160
won't favor you.

161
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,280
What if

162
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,680
I conceive an imperial child?

163
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,960
With just you?

164
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,120
Without me,

165
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,040
you couldn't even get near him.

166
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,120
You were near him,

167
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:43,200
yet you haven't given
birth to a single child.

168
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,200
You...

169
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,480
Fourth Young Lady Jiang,

170
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:49,200
Her Majesty is so ill,

171
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,560
yet she stayed up
this late for your sake.

172
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:52,720
Instead of being grateful,

173
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,280
you're upsetting Her Majesty.

174
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,080
I can no longer control you.

175
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,520
Shun,

176
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,000
let's go.

177
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:12,160
(I put a whole bottle
of Love Potion in it.)

178
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,480
(I don't believe)

179
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,200
(the Emperor can resist it.)

180
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,840
The tea is drugged.

181
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,640
What audacity.

182
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,880
I'm here to serve Your Majesty.

183
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,480
Your Majesty...

184
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,400
Jiang Wanning,

185
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,600
for your insubordination,

186
00:12:01,610 --> 00:12:02,830
you are expelled from the palace.

187
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,720
You shall never set foot
in the palace again.

188
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,680
Your Majesty,

189
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,920
come back!

190
00:12:17,540 --> 00:12:21,220
♪Moon sets on palace walls,
breeze hits the gates♪

191
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,680
Your Majesty.

192
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:30,140
♪Falling at first sight,
a life of turmoil wasted♪

193
00:12:31,230 --> 00:12:37,380
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

194
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:43,860
♪All the spring colors
lean toward one person♪

195
00:12:44,890 --> 00:12:48,940
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

196
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,080
Your Majesty.

197
00:12:52,660 --> 00:12:55,860
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

198
00:12:56,020 --> 00:12:59,660
♪The world is gentle
only because of you♪

199
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:02,620
♪In the palace, through dawn and dusk,
who keeps a lamp burning♪

200
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:08,780
♪Time silently scars those left behind♪

201
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:23,220
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

202
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:30,180
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

203
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:34,180
♪If we don't meet♪

204
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:37,620
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

205
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:44,340
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

206
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:51,140
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

207
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:57,820
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

208
00:13:58,340 --> 00:14:05,020
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

209
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:11,900
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

210
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:18,020
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

211
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:25,540
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

212
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:32,380
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

213
00:14:32,660 --> 00:14:39,100
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

